<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 12:28:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于中国市场压力，杰尼亚第三季度销售额下降 7%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ermenegildo-zegna-sales-down-7-third-quarter-china-weighs-2024-10-22/</link><description>意大利奢侈品集团杰尼亚 (Ermenegildo Zegna) 周二表示，受大中华区收入下降 22% 的影响，该公司第三季度的有机收入下降了 6.7%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 11:40:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ermenegildo-zegna-sales-down-7-third-quarter-china-weighs-2024-10-22/</guid></item><item><title>券商上调中国2024年GDP增​​长预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/brokerages-raise-china-gdp-growth-estimates-2024-2024-10-22/</link><description>官方数据显示，中国经济 7 月至 9 月增长 4.6%，为 2023 年初以来的最低增速，低于第二季度 4.7% 的增速，房地产行业的暴跌仍然是北京面临的主要挑战。</description><pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 11:08:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/brokerages-raise-china-gdp-growth-estimates-2024-2024-10-22/</guid></item><item><title>为应对中国封锁，台湾制定战时粮食计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/preparing-chinese-blockade-taiwan-maps-out-wartime-food-plans-2024-10-22/</link><description>台湾政府周二罕见地提供了战时粮食计划的细节，称其正在每月盘点大米等重要物资，并确保它们在全岛妥善储存，以防中国封锁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 10:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/preparing-chinese-blockade-taiwan-maps-out-wartime-food-plans-2024-10-22/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：债券大跌，国际货币基金组织预测到期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-10-22/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 10:09:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-10-22/</guid></item><item><title>由于即将到来的选举引发关税担忧，美国出口商竞相运输大豆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-exporters-race-ship-soybeans-looming-election-stokes-tariff-worries-2024-10-22/</link><description>交易商和分析师表示，美国大豆出口溢价创下 14 个月以来的最高水平，原因是粮商在美国总统大选前竞相运送创纪录的美国收成，并且担心与最大进口国中国的贸易紧张局势再度紧张。</description><pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 10:05:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-exporters-race-ship-soybeans-looming-election-stokes-tariff-worries-2024-10-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国的“双十一”促销节未能激发消费者的兴趣</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-singles-day-sales-festival-fails-inspire-consumers-2024-10-22/</link><description>中国最大的购物活动正在进行中，但大多数商家和零售分析师预计销售增长将持平或充其量是不温不火，并指出消费者仍然对中国的经济困境感到非常沮丧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 09:23:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-singles-day-sales-festival-fails-inspire-consumers-2024-10-22/</guid></item><item><title>降雨过多导致印度棉花产量下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-cotton-output-fall-lower-area-excess-rain-trade-body-says-2024-10-22/</link><description>一家主要贸易机构周二表示，由于面积减少以及过量降雨损害了作物，印度2024/25年度棉花产量可能较上年同期下降7.4%至3020万包。</description><pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 08:57:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-cotton-output-fall-lower-area-excess-rain-trade-body-says-2024-10-22/</guid></item><item><title>恒大称深交所对其子公司、创始人实施制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrande-says-shenzhen-stock-exchange-finds-its-unit-others-violation-2024-10-22/</link><description>中国恒大清算人周二表示，深圳证券交易所已对该房地产开发商的旗舰子公司恒大地产及其创始人许家印等高级管理人员发布纪律处分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 08:46:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrande-says-shenzhen-stock-exchange-finds-its-unit-others-violation-2024-10-22/</guid></item><item><title>ASML首席执行官表示，预计2026年将实现增长，中美争端将持续</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-ceo-says-us-pressure-export-restrictions-will-continue-2024-10-22/</link><description>领先计算机芯片设备制造商ASML首席执行官周二表示，预计2026年将是该公司的增长年，美国政府将继续推动对其对华出口实施进一步限制。</description><pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 08:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-ceo-says-us-pressure-export-restrictions-will-continue-2024-10-22/</guid></item><item><title>梵蒂冈与中国延长天主教主教任命协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-it-has-extended-agreement-with-vatican-bishops-2024-10-22/</link><description>中国和梵蒂冈周二表示，双方已同意将这个共产主义国家天主教主教任命协议延长四年。</description><pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 08:21:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-it-has-extended-agreement-with-vatican-bishops-2024-10-22/</guid></item><item><title>Cheniere Energy预计到2040年中国天然气需求将增长50%以上</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/cheniere-energy-expects-china-gas-demand-rise-more-than-50-by-2040-2024-10-22/</link><description>Cheniere Energy 公司高管周二在亚洲天然气市场会议上表示，预计到 2040 年，中国天然气需求将从目前的 400 立方米增至超过 6000 亿立方米。</description><pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 08:03:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/cheniere-energy-expects-china-gas-demand-rise-more-than-50-by-2040-2024-10-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国确认解决与印度边界冲突的协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-implement-solutions-with-india-resolving-border-conflict-2024-10-22/</link><description>中国周二证实，已与印度就有争议的边界达成协议，但没有详细说明该协议是否涵盖整个边界，还是仅涵盖双方自 2020 年以来陷入对峙的地点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 07:26:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-implement-solutions-with-india-resolving-border-conflict-2024-10-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国需求疲软阻碍了假日酒店所有者洲际酒店集团第三季度的发展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/holiday-inn-owner-ihgs-third-quarter-room-revenue-grows-15-2024-10-22/</link><description>假日酒店所有者洲际酒店集团报告称，由于中国需求疲软和美国市场低迷掩盖了欧洲的稳健表现，第三季度客房收入增长急剧放缓。</description><pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 06:12:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/holiday-inn-owner-ihgs-third-quarter-room-revenue-grows-15-2024-10-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国推出首个诊断指南应对不断升级的肥胖危机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-unveils-first-diagnosis-guidelines-battle-escalating-obesity-crisis-2024-10-22/</link><description>中国国家卫生健康委员会（NHC）发布了第一套规范肥胖诊断和治疗的指南，中国一半以上的成年人已经超重和肥胖，并且这一比例预计将继续上升。</description><pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 05:25:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-unveils-first-diagnosis-guidelines-battle-escalating-obesity-crisis-2024-10-22/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯官方媒体奉承特朗普，但克里姆林宫对他和哈里斯态度冷淡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/russian-state-media-flatters-trump-kremlin-cool-him-harris-2024-10-22/</link><description>特朗普在乌克兰对俄战争中的公开支持程度要低得多。</description><pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 05:03:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/russian-state-media-flatters-trump-kremlin-cool-him-harris-2024-10-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>